## Order (do not skip)

**P0 — will break or harm**
- Security: injection, IDOR, secret leaks
- Data loss risk
- Races, leaks

**P1 — hurts maintainability**
- Violates patterns in `patterns.md`
- Functions > ~40 lines or mixed responsibilities
- Unsafe typing (`any`, forced assertions)
- Duplication (extract on the third copy)

**P2 — nice to have**
- Unclear names
- Deletable code
- Performance issues with evidence

## Output format
`[P0] path:line — issue + one-line fix`  
`[P1] path:line — issue + one-line fix`  
`[P2]` — one short paragraph if more than five items, else list briefly

Say **LGTM** if nothing to flag; do not pad the answer.
